settings.title: How can I order?
settings.answer:
First you find the products you need and simply add them to the cart.

To place the actual order, you need to have an account and log in.

If you do not have an account, you can still request a quote from the cart - and we will get back to you.

settings.title: How to get an account?
settings.answer: To get an account, please contact us via the Contact form - and we can have a dialogue and set you up.

settings.title: Why do I not see product prices?
settings.answer:
To get access to your prices, you need to have an account and log in.

Contact us to be set up.

settings.title: Why are the delivery times on many products "On request"?
settings.answer:
For products in stock, we have a short delivery time..

For products that are not in stock, the delivery times can vary.

So to secure the most accurate and fast delivery time, we recommend to contact us.

settings.title: Did you not find the answer?
settings.content: If you could not find the answer, you were looking for - please reach out, and we will support you!
